Alembic migrations for Shining Horizon backend.

Run from backend/ directory:

  alembic current                          # show current DB revision
  alembic upgrade head                     # apply all pending migrations
  alembic downgrade -1                     # roll back one migration
  alembic history                          # list all migrations
  alembic revision -m "what you changed"   # create empty migration
  alembic revision --autogenerate -m "..." # auto-detect schema diffs

Migration files live in alembic/versions/. Always review autogenerated
migrations before committing — autogenerate is a starting point, not gospel.
